WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.110
From the land of exceptionally sophisticated
nuclear energy systems.

00:00:04.110 --> 00:00:08.200
And the world's first deep geological
repository of spent nuclear fuel.

00:00:08.200 --> 00:00:13.030
With over 90% annual load factor
in nuclear power plants.

00:00:13.030 --> 00:00:17.140
You now find also world's most
modern centre for nuclear safety.

00:00:18.080 --> 00:00:22.160
Microscopy - Revealing the mechanisms of
material performance.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:29.020
Control room - Expertise in human
factors engineering.

00:00:30.070 --> 00:00:34.220
Hot Cell - Irradiated materials research
for plant life management.

00:00:38.020 --> 00:00:41.160
Hot Cell - Materials performance
testing for safe operation.

00:00:41.160 --> 00:00:46.200
Bentonite - Barrier material for
spent-fuel repository.

00:00:46.200 --> 00:00:52.080
Bentonite - Early-age and long-term
performance testing.

00:00:54.130 --> 00:01:02.080
Bentonite - Groundwater composition research

00:01:02.080 --> 00:01:06.230
NDE Testing - Non-destructive testing of
spent nuclear fuel canister components.

00:01:06.230 --> 00:01:12.140
Waste Management - Expertise to study
long-term safety of nuclear waste disposal.

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:18.140
With its 200 nuclear safety experts.

00:01:18.220 --> 00:01:21.090
VTT is the biggest nuclear R&D and technical
Support organisation in Northern Europe.

00:01:21.160 --> 00:01:23.050
And we are ready to cooperate
